Package: speccurvieR
Type: Package
Title: Easy, Fast, and Pretty Specification Curve Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zayne", "Sember", email = "zsember@ucsd.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: speccurvieR is an R package aimed at making specification curve 
  analysis easy, fast, and pretty. It improves upon existing offerings with
  additional features and tidyverse integration. Users can easily visualize and
  evaluate how their models behave under different specifications with a high
  degree of customization.
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
